b. Instruct the Municipal Accountant for the immediate submission of the unsubmitted delayed financial reports and documents. Moreover, give utmost priority in the preparation of monthly BRS and submit to the audit team all BRS due for submission;

c. Provide control on the proper handling and accountabilities of disbursement vouchers and supporting documents to prevent loss of documents and facilitate prompt submission of reports; and

d. Enjoin the Municipal Accountant to strictly enforce the submission of succeeding required financial reports and accounts within the prescribed period.

